---
title: Venison & Beef Rissoles with Kumara Fries, Caramelised Onion & Garlic Aioli
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing winner, but when you cover them with cheese and sweet caramelised onion, they’re even
harder to refuse! This colourful plate also gets a serve of kumara fries and a family-friendly salad for a rainbow of delights.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-rissoles-fries-c2b8e05d.jpg
